{"tid":1275183,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］文宣組入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-01T18:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T19:44:40.000Z","uid":231015,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"be0ad0e7085e297ed701c674ff83401093a5f04c","tid":1275183,"uid":231015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:30:13.000Z","msg":"辛苦你哋咁多日嘅付出啦<br />\n但係我哋仲有好長嘅路要走<br />\n<br />\n今次嘅輿論十分重要<br />\n首先全部黨媒一定鋪天蓋地放大衝立會嘅行為<br />\n重點係部分和理非對於衝立會都開有啲怨言<br />\n泛民亦都俾人施壓要割蓆<br />\n<br />\n先唔好屌任何一方先<br />\n宜家首要任務係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>穩住+挽回民心，唔可以俾佢哋有任何機會割蓆</strong></span><br />\n要知道咁多次以嚟都係靠大家合作先可以叫做暫緩下<br />\n如果今次無埋佢哋嘅支持<br />\n之後一定難行好多<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n我哋要主動帶返風向<br />\n講返五大訴求<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（+點解要衝?） </span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好俾人放大衝立會嘅行為</span></strong><br />\n小弟不才諗唔到啲咩<br />\n大家一齊幫幫手啦<br />\n輿論靠我哋㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>千祈唔好互屌，關鍵時刻最緊要團結！香港人加油！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"c7b40fd5765719ec79f540f70cec54d6ce1893c8","tid":1275183,"uid":231015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:30:40.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"093a64423d5d695aba3b5c0685cb5e37466438a2","tid":1275183,"uid":231015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:30:50.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ebea217ef0bf0fe7007d3f4cec6f40e5ffb21db2","tid":1275183,"uid":231015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:31:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b71459ccb17b288f7c266f33520ecfb1deceb412","tid":1275183,"uid":231015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:31:14.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2a25154ec53fee0f6bc006e8eec9f93242cd604d","tid":1275183,"uid":231015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:31:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9c64bfb1ab7f2f8ec53a221c3e8b90018925dec4","tid":1275183,"uid":231015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T1